ct','Nouveau mot de passe pour votre compte sur {PAGE_TITLE}',0,NULL,0,12,16),(5018,4,'wcf.acp.user.sendActivationMail','Envoyer un e-mail dactivation aux utilisateurs',0,NULL,0,12,16),(5019,4,'wcf.acp.user.sendNewPassword','Envoyer un nouveau mot de passe aux utilisateurs',0,NULL,0,12,16),(5020,4,'wcf.acp.user.unban.success','Le bannissement des utilisateur a bien t retir.',0,NULL,0,12,16),(5021,4,'wcf.help.item.moderation','Moderation',0,NULL,0,24,16),(5022,4,'wcf.help.item.moderation.description','<p>Like administrators moderators have special rights so they can edit and delete content from other users. To use the moderative functions the browser needs enabled JavaScript.{if $allItemNames[\'board\']|isset} At <a href=\"index.php?form=UserProfileEdit{@SID_ARG_2ND}\">Edit profile</a> &raquo; <a href=\"index.php?page=ModerationOverview{@SID_ARG_2ND}\">Moderation</a> you will find an overview about moderation.{/if} The moderation options are presented in the following.</p>',0,NULL,0,24,16),(5023,4,'wcf.help.item.user','User account (Profile)',0,NULL,0,24,16),(5024,4,'wcf.help.item.user.data','Personal data',0,NULL,0,24,16),(5025,4,'wcf.help.item.user.data.description','<p class=\"helpImage border container-4\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"{@RELATIVE_WCF_DIR}images/help/helpUserData1.png\" /><span class=\"smallFont light\">Personal data</span></p>\n<p>You can enter personal information, that can be seen by other members, under <a href=\"index.php?form=UserProfileEdit{@SID_ARG_2ND}\">Edit profile</a>. This information is usually optional e.g. contact data.</p>\n<p>Under <a href=\"index.php?form=AccountManagement{@SID_ARG_2ND}\">Edit account</a> you can change the access data for this user account:</p>\n<ol>\n	<li>The username you need to login to this page.</li>\n	<li>The password you also need to login.</li>\n	<li>The e-mail address thats connected to this user account.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Furthermore you can delete the user account with all personal data. Created content though cannot be deleted.</p>',0,NULL,0,24,16),(5026,4,'wcf.help.item.user.description','<p>To use all features you need to register your own user account on this page.</p>',0,NULL,0,24,16),(5027,4,'wcf.help.item.user.login','Registration and login',0,NULL,0,24,16),(5028,4,'wcf.help.item.user.login.description','<h4>Registration</h4>\n<p>If you want to create your own account on this page, follow the <a href=\"index.php?page=Register{@SID_ARG_2ND}\">Register</a> link in the menu. After accepting the {if \'MODULE_RULE\'|defined}<a href=\"index.php?page=Rules{@SID_ARG_2ND}\">terms and conditions</a>{else}terms and conditions{/if}, you will need to enter some personal information:</p>\n<p class=\"helpImage border container-4\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"{@RELATIVE_WCF_DIR}images/help/helpUserLogin2.png\" /><span class=\"smallFont light\">Captcha image</span></p>\n<ol>\n	<li>Username - This is the name you will use to login. Usernames are unique, if your username is already taken, you will have to choose a different one.</li>\n	<li>Password - Please select a secure password, and try to change it as often as possible.</li>\n	<li>E-mail address - Your e-mail address must be unique as well.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>It is possible that other fields need to be filled out as well. The <a href=\"http://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Captcha\" class=\"externalURL\">captcha image</a> protects the page against spam robots. You have to write the letters you can see on the image into the related text field. You can recreate and enlarge the image if you have difficulties reading it. If you do not manage to complete that step you can contact an administrator.</p>\n<h4>Login</h4>\n<p class=\"helpImage border container-4\"><img src=\"{@RELATIVE_WCF_DIR}images/help/helpUserLogin1.png\" alt=\"\" /><span class=\"smallFont light\">Login window</span></p>\n<p>With an existing user account you can login to the page. Click on the menu item <a href=\"index.php?form=Login{@SID_ARG_2ND}\">Login</a> and enter your username and password. If you have forgotten your password you can use the <a href=\"index.php?form=LostPassword{@SID_ARG_2ND}\">Forgot password</a> function. You will have to enter either your e-mail or your username. If your account has not been <a href=\"index.php?page=Register&action=enable{@SID_ARG_2ND}\">activated</a> yet you will have to go to the <a href=\"index.php?form=Login{@SID_ARG_2ND}\">login page</a>.</p>',0,NULL,0,24,16),(5029,4,'wcf.help.item.user.settings','Settings',0,NULL,0,24,16),(5030,4,'wcf.help.item.user.settings.description','<p class=\"helpImage border container-4\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"{@RELATIVE_WCF_DIR}images/help/helpUserSettings1.png\" /><span class=\"smallFont light\">Settings</span></p>\n<p>Under <a href=\"index.php?form=UserProfileEdit{@SID_ARG_2ND}\">Edit Profile</a> &raquo; <a href=\"index.php?form=UserProfileEdit&category=settings.general{@SID_ARG_2ND}\">Settings</a> you can choose from several options to make the use of this page comfortable for you.</p>\n<p>Next to general settings - e.g. your timezone - you will find options for privacy, communication and display. Please note that these settings just apply to your account.</p>',0,NULL,0,24,16),(5031,4,'wcf.user.banned','Your user account has been banned permanently {if $this->user->banReason}with the following reason: {$this->user->banReason}{/if}.',0,NULL,0,17,16),(5032,4,'wcf.user.edit.success','Vos modifications ont bien t enregistres.',0,NULL,0,17,16),(5033,4,'wcf.user.error.password.notSecure','Your password is too short. \n		For security reasons the password should contain at least {REGISTER_PASSWORD_MIN_LENGTH} characters{if REGISTER_PASSWORD_MUST_CONTAIN_LOWER_CASE || REGISTER_PASSWORD_MUST_CONTAIN_UPPER_CASE || REGISTER_PASSWORD_MUST_CONTAIN_DIGIT || REGISTER_PASSWORD_MUST_CONTAIN_SPECIAL_CHAR}\n		and\n		{if REGISTER_PASSWORD_MUST_CONTAIN_LOWER_CASE}small letters{/if}{*\n		*}{if REGISTER_PASSWORD_MUST_CONTAIN_UPPER_CASE}{if REGISTER_PASSWORD_MUST_CONTAIN_LOWER_CASE}{if REGISTER_PASS